 Precious Achiuwa is up for the NBA draft.  If that happens, it would set a new African record, breaking the record set in 2016. The African players on the window are Mamadi Diakite (Guinea), Precious Achiuwa (Nigeria), Udoka Azubuike (Nigeria), Paul Eboua (Cameroon), Karim Mane (Senegal), and Lamine Diane (Senegal).  Precious Achiuwa spoke to media last night and shared his excitement about being able to follow the footsteps of two-time NBA champion Hakeem Olajuwon and other great Nigerian players in the NBA.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .